additional_house_rules:
• Check-in time is 3PM.

• EARLY CHECK-IN / LATE CHECK-OUT •
Exceptions can be made on a case by case basis for each guest/reservation. If needed then please specifically ask if it will be possible on your travel dates.
---------------------------------------------------------
• EVENING CHECK-IN •
If you are planning on arriving at the apartment after 6 PM then you must let me know in advance so that I can plan accordingly and make sure you will have access to the apartment once you arrive.
---------------------------------------------------------
• LUGGAGE STORAGE •
If the schedule allows for it then it may be possible to leave bags at the apartment for short amounts of time after the official 10 AM check-out, however I'm generally not able to provide luggage storage for extended amounts of time. For example, if your flight doesn't leave until much later in the evening then you must make other arrangements to keep your bags somewhere other than in the apartment.
I'm happy to try and help as best I can but if I'm not able to then I can also direct you to some luggage storage services in the neighborhood that aren't far from the apartment.
---------------------------------------------------------
!!! THIS IS A NON-SMOKING APARTMENT !!!
That means there is absolutely no smoking allowed whatsoever in the apartment, in the stairwells, or anywhere else in the building. You are more than welcome to smoke outside in front of the building, however please be considerate of the neighbors when doing so.
If a guest was found to have been smoking in the apartment it will result in losing the ENTIRE security deposit, no questions asked. DO NOT try to spray air freshener everywhere to cover it up, I promise you I will know.
description:
The apartment is right off of 8th Avenue near all of your favorite places to go!
Perfect for tourism in one of NYC's most desirable neighborhoods of Hell's Kitchen! Just a short walk to Time's Sq, Rockefeller Center, Bryan Park, Empire St. Bldg, Broadway, steps to the train, many of the best landmarks, restaurants, bars, shopping and more!

PLEASE click "contact host" BEFORE "request to book"

Before submitting a reservation requests (by clicking "request to book") please make sure that you have first:
- sent me a message directly (by clicking "contact host" below the reviews)
and I have written you back and confirmed availability
- read through the entire listing
- read through the "house rules" section
Any reservation request that is sent over without messaging me first I will ask to be declined automatically.
Thanks!
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
• Newly remodeled, fully furnished one bedroom apartment
• Spacious, bright, and super clean
• Kitchen has all appliances and utensils (stove/oven, refrigerator, microwave, coffee maker, pots, pans, plates, bowls, etc)
• Brand new Queen-size bed, probably one of the most comfortable ones you'll sleep in away from home 
• Newly renovated, super clean bathroom
• The apartment is on the 7th floor of a elevator building.

• High-speed WiFi / cable TV
• Sheets, towels, pillows, blankets (extra bedding if needed)
• Air conditioning, heat, and plenty of hot water
• Pots, pans, plates, bowls, cups, and cooking utensils
• Iron and ironing board
• A personal touch of service and attention for every one of my guests!

You will have the entire apartment to yourself, it is a non shared, private unit. I'm here to make your stay as comfortable and enjoyable as possible. Anything that I can help you with, from restaurant recommendations, to entertainment, I am happy to share my personal favorite picks.

• 2 blocks from Times Square (5 min walk)
• 1 block from the subway (1 min walk)
• 20 minute walk to Central Park
• Right near 9th Ave, which is just one long stretch of restaurants, cafes, bars, etc one after the other for about 30 blocks.
• Vibrant Hell's Kitchen neighborhood, clean, safe, full of energy, and close to great transportation options.

My apartment is very, very close to the subway to literally get you anywhere you'd like or need to go!

Please note that for privacy purposes the listing only shows an APPROXIMATE street/location within 1 - 2 blocks of the apartment. The full correct address is sent out once a reservation has been booked. This is done to protect the privacy/safety of both my guests as well as myself.
